column5: Got a great offer to spend this weekend at a cottage on the island.  Although I think she is just using me for a ride to the island I'm determined to come back smelling of fish one way or the other!  I understand the landscape but the couch is new to me. Any pointers?
so you ever work the couch or not?
Are you targeting bass? Hit the lower end.Tubes and spinners bait.Sight fish.If you find deep cabbage,burn spinner baits,or resort to jigs,and rip them through the cabbage.
Hit the lower end.   that's all I needed to hear      What do you think, work the southern bays?
WORK YOUR WAY AND LEARN.JUST LIKE I DID.
Sorry for the double entendre, I had a case of drunk posting yesterday.
This post is like one of those "romantic novels" that all the women read!!! LMAO!
May I'll write one call "50 Shades of Tube Jigs!"
